</svg>
</span><p>When you're ready, search your state's small business website using the terms "property management" or "real estate" to find out if there are any special property management company requirements that apply to your business.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-property-management-business-section5-step2" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>5.2&nbsp;</span><h4 id=apply-for-the-license-and-or-permit>Apply for the license and/or permit.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-apply-for-the-license-and-or-permit-288x288-20200922.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Apply for the license and/or permit."></div></div><p>In most cases, you can submit and pay for your application online.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-property-management-business-section6" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
<span>6.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=purchase-insurance>Purchase insurance.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-property-management-business-section6-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>6.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=determine-what-risks-you-039-ll-be-exposed-to>Determine what risks you&#039;ll be exposed to.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-determine-what-risks-you-will-be-exposed-to-288x288-20200819.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Determine what risks you&#039;ll be exposed to."></div></div><p>Property management companies operate in a space that is heavy with liability issues. Any group that is given the responsibility of maintaining a property must be aware that they are in the care of a valuable physical asset that could be destroyed or damaged by weather, fire, vandalism, or some other accident.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-property-management-business-section6-step2" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>6.2&nbsp;</span><h4 id=purchase-the-relevant-insurance>Purchase the relevant insurance.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-purchase-the-relevant-insurance-288x288-20200819.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Purchase the relevant insurance."></div></div><p>Your property management company should purchase several types of insurance, including:</p><ul><li>Liability insurance.</li><li>Commerical property insurance.</li><li>Business interruption insurance.</li><li>Automobile insurance.</li></ul><div
class="step-tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>You can contact an insurance provider or broker to request a quote for your property management company. A representative will be able to give you more information based on the details that you provide them about your business.</p></div><div
class="step-tip">
<span
class="icon">
