</g>
</svg>
</span><p>Major business insurance providers like Liberty Mutual and The Hartford offer special real estate insurance packages that are designed for property management companies. You may want to ask about these.</p></div></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-property-management-business-section7" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
<span>7.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=find-an-office>Find an office.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-property-management-business-section7-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>7.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=decide-whether-to-work-from-home-or-a-commercial-space>Decide whether to work from home or a commercial space.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-consider-whether-to-work-from-home-or-a-commercial-space-288x288-20200819-1.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Decide whether to work from home or a commercial space."></div></div><p>It might be possible to start a property management business in your home, but with photocopiers, phones, employees and records, you may find it easier to have a commercial office space.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-property-management-business-section7-step2" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>7.2&nbsp;</span><h4 id=choose-whether-to-rent-or-purchase-a-commercial-space>Choose whether to rent or purchase a commercial space.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-choose-whether-to-rent-or-purchase-a-commercial-space-288x288-20200819.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Choose whether to rent or purchase a commercial space."></div></div><p>You can either purchase a building or rent an office. Most property management startups opt to lease space because it is more affordable and gives them flexibility if their needs change.</p><div
class="step-tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>WeWork and similar companies offer a shared workplace solutions that are worth considering.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-property-management-business-section7-step3" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>7.3&nbsp;</span><h4 id=search-for-an-office>Search for an office.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-search-for-an-office-288x288-20200819.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Search for an office."></div></div><p>Meet with a real estate agent or consult online listings to find out what is available. If you need an office that can be easily visited by customers, find a location that is in your local business district or town center. Property management companies are always dealing with tenants, utility companies, and tradespeople, so you will probably want an office that is easy for these parties to visit.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-property-management-business-section8" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
<span>8.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=advertise-your-business>Advertise your business.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-property-management-business-section8-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>8.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=create-a-company-website>Create a company website.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-create-a-company-website-288x288-20200819.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Create a company website."></div></div><p><a
href="https://www.zarla.com/guides/how-to-register-a-domain-name">Register a domain name</a> and build a site that explains who you are and what you offer. Having a website will increase your visibility and legitimacy.</p><div
class="step-tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
